{"tid":2098115,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「國安法如金箍兒」  古德明擱筆《蘋果》論壇","createTime":"2020-07-07T09:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T16:54:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6827b8f0c12a1c80bfbf09f2119f6c0496be8fd6","tid":2098115,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:02:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200707/4KRSA4O2OS7EGCKO67A4TAL36A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2F4KRSA4O2OS7EGCKO67A4TAL36A%2F&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivQTszQqcSrFeuHGFn5Djw6E%3D&h=0e2ebc07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2F4KRSA4O2OS7EGCKO67A4TAL36A%2F&h=22f92171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200707/4KRSA4O2OS7EGCKO67A4TAL36A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「國安法如金箍兒」  古德明擱筆《蘋果》論壇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qdJV-xoG3NHV8Uft3RX8o7rk8kw=/640x392/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RQART2DQJU5GYTI5DLGSYEKUXY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqdJV-xoG3NHV8Uft3RX8o7rk8kw%3D%2F640x392%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRQART2DQJU5GYTI5DLGSYEKUXY.jpg&h=806c5a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古德明昨於專欄宣佈停止在本報論壇版撰文。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】白色恐怖隨含糊不清的港區國安<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n除非習近平落台囉」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：逼網絡商提供用戶身份<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「呢種恐懼大家都有」<br />\n<br />\n「六月三十日，中共通過『港區國安法』，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n停止在論壇版撰文。<br />\n<br />\n他解釋，港人有敢違反國安法，監禁輕則三年，重則終身，「在這大精神之下，我怎能不告別論壇版。」他質疑，根據港區國安法，令人「憎恨」中共中央政府或香港地方政府，都可問罪，「然則照事實陳述香港公安私刑市民，是不是也算令人『憎恨』香港當局？」<br />\n<br />\n文章又引用東周楚昏王的歷史故事，昏王力求統一思想，結果「正言不發，萬口如封；諂媚相與，千顏一容」。<br />\n<br />\n現年66歲的古德明生於中山石岐，曾任職《明報月刊》總編輯，1997年曾隨家人移民新西蘭。他接受《蘋果》訪問時，劈頭第一句苦笑道：「冇得寫啦！邊有得寫箒。」他解釋，平日自己最喜愛寫中文、寫政治，但現時寫政治動輒得咎，「批評兩句大陸共產黨，批評兩句林鄭月娥，你都可以話煽動憎恨&hellip;&hellip;批評同煽動，你點分？」<br />\n<br />\n為《蘋果》論壇獻筆21年，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n他續說，對國安法實施後的香港前景感到悲觀，希望中共及港府明白「再咁搞落去實死」，「一個月前我諗大家都冇諗過搞到今日咁，除非習近平落台囉。」<br />\n<br />\n古德明於《蘋果》論壇版的「常山月旦」即將暫停，而生活名采版的「東拼西湊」則照常，但他今後會「寫啲冇咁政治嘅嘢」。"},{"pid":"27fe4b06567bf13540e7b416a8489a68e5c1ca4e","tid":2098115,"uid":46906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:04:17.000Z","msg":"佢講得無錯，總加速師去到最後一步就係加速到佢自己都做唔住要落台"},{"pid":"4f695e4271d6deb860bfe18b8ac450c7d624314c","tid":2098115,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:05:42.000Z","msg":"佢寫啲嘢好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d12ea571a1d126df8961fc6657b43cbdabfc58f","tid":2098115,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:06:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>近日新增大量本地確診</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家出街一定要戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n勤力洗手<br />\n<br />\n唔好去人多既地方</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">希望政府可以立即停課，收緊限聚令，停gym房，戲院，k房等</span></span>"},{"pid":"016a0a975d03d77c1cc01f9b7b01ae5c5fb74939","tid":2098115,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:07:20.000Z","msg":"個擱字用得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1031bb19dc6973d3c728b8168916ad18eb6296e","tid":2098115,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T16:54:12.000Z","msg":"可惜"}]}